ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to (1) eliminate regulatory redundancy by repealing the existing provisions in the Regulations that govern the federal Investor and Entrepreneur Programs; (2) provide for a transitional period as those programs wind down; and (3) leave a regulatory framework in place for the continued operation of Quebec’s programs.
